# Ferbee Privacy Policy

**Effective Date: July 1, 2025

Ferbee does not collect or transmit any personal data.

- All data you enter (such as baby name, sleep logs, preferences) is stored **locally on your device**.
- Ferbee **does not connect to the internet** or send data to any server.
- You remain the sole owner of all your data.
- You can erase your data at any time using the **"Reset All Data"** button in the app's Settings.

We value your privacy. If you have any concerns or questions, feel free to contact us at: **helloferbee@gmail.com**
